*hypre-2.7.0b (19 Mar 2011)

  19 Mar 2011; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  hypre-2.6.0b.ebuild, -files/hypre-2.6.0b-makefile.patch,
  +hypre-2.7.0b.ebuild, +files/makefile-mpicxx.patch:
  Added new ebuild of hypre version 2.7.0b
  moved makefile mpicxx patch to version-independen name since it
  applies to the new version too.

  24 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  hypre-2.6.0b.ebuild:
  using original hypre download link instead of charon-suite third-party
  packages

  24 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  -hypre-2.4.0b-r1.ebuild, -files/hypre-2.4.0b-soname.patch,
  hypre-2.6.0b.ebuild, +files/hypre-2.6.0b-makefile.patch:
  removed non-working 2.4 tree
  fixed mpi and lapack dependencies
  fixed linking (introducing ${P}-makefile.patch)

*hypre-2.4.0b-r1 (14 Nov 2010)

  14 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  -hypre-2.4.0b.ebuild, +hypre-2.4.0b-r1.ebuild,
  files/hypre-2.4.0b-soname.patch:
  first try to rework ebuild (fix undefined references) - not yet working

  13 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  +hypre-2.4.0b.ebuild, +files/hypre-2.4.0b-soname.patch:
  added hypre version 2.4 since e.g. petsc does not work with recent 2.6
  version

*hypre-2.4.0b (13 Nov 2010)

  13 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  +hypre-2.4.0b.ebuild:
  added new ebuild for hypre 2.4 release

  13 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  hypre-2.6.0b.ebuild:
  removed python use flag without effect

*hypre-2.6.0b (13 Nov 2010)

  13 Nov 2010; Jens-Malte Gottfried <jmgottfried@web.de>
  +hypre-2.6.0b.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  new ebuild: hypre parallel high performance preconditioner for linear
  systems

